[Name "Expert Use of the Rooks"]
[Subtitle ""]
[Description "It's quite easy to learn how the rook moves, but to use it correctly is much more complicated. In a minute you will be a master of rooks!"]
[Tags "basics,open-file,seventh-rank"]
